    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in today's used car market. Every aspect of this car has been meticulously maintained, from the pristine exterior finish that shows no scratches, dents, or paint fade, to the spotless interior that looks and smells virtually new. Mechanically, the engine runs flawlessly, all systems function as intended, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises to report. The tires have excellent tread remaining, all electronics and features work perfectly, and the vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled environment. Service records are up to date, and this car is ready to drive home with complete confidence. This is the kind of used car that buyers rarely come across \u2014 one that genuinely requires no immediate investment beyond fuel.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
