      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 as close to showroom-perfect as a used car can be. The exterior is flawless, with paint that retains its original deep luster, no scratches, dents, dings, or blemishes of any kind. Every panel aligns perfectly, and the chrome and trim pieces are spotless. The interior is immaculate \u2014 the seats, carpets, headliner, and dashboard show absolutely no wear, fading, or damage, looking and smelling fresh as the day it left the factory. All electronics, controls, and comfort features function perfectly without exception. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power; there are no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. The tires have excellent tread remaining and are evenly worn, and the brakes are in top condition. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly requires nothing \u2014 no repairs, no cosmetic touch-ups, no surprises. A full service history is available. Ideal for a discerning buyer who wants the best.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
